    .content-centered
      %h1 Speakers
      .row
        .content-centered
          %p The speakers involved are well known and come from near and far. They'll share life experiences, technical stories, and cultural successes & failures.
          %p.line-through  Dying to know who's going to be speaking? We'll announce a speaker after we raise $800 for Nairobi Dev School and each $300 thereafter.
          %h2 Impressive!
          %p Just when you thought you had unlocked all the the speakers, <strong>a Boss appears!</strong> He has 600 hit points. When we hit <strong>$3000</strong> our final speaker will be announced!
